[normal]Longframlington[bold] Parish Council, Northumberland[bold] (TIC 054)[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]The councillors would like to wholeheartedly support the thoughtful letter supplied below and hope that notice is taken of the need to consider rural services as a network not just as isolated services.  
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Running a [bold]rural transport network in such a sparsely populated area as Northumberland is completely different to an urban one. Rural needs are more basic and exceptionally community related.  [bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
